title: Wilson Federer Pro Staff Precision XL 110 Gloss Red Tennis Racquet in Grip Size 4 3/8" Bundled with a Pink Advantage II Tennis Bag (Incredible Feel and Control)
description: The Wilson Federer Pro Staff Precision XL 110 packs a vibrant red punch of game improvement characteristics for recreational players. At 11.5 oz (326 g) strung with an oversize 110-sq-in head, this frame carries plenty of power with some margin for error on strokes that miss the center of the string bed. Its aluminum composition lends a durable feel, and its extra length gives players more time to make a play on the next ball with extended court coverage. The sharp design and precision performance is inspired by the Pro Staff performance series of tennis racquets endorsed by Roger Federer. Head Size: 110 sq in String Pattern: 16x19 Strung Weight: 326 g Length: 27.25 in - 69.2 cm Player Type: Recreational & Beginner The Wilson Advantage II Tennis Racket Bag in is an inexpensive, yet well-made way of carrying up to 2 tennis racquets onto the court with you. The bag is made of a sturdy canvass material and weighs 13 ounces, so it won't be too heavy to carry. It fits both shorter junior frames, as well as standard adult racket frames. The neutral colors will be desirable to boys, girls, men, and women alike.
